title: Cardio Machines, Full Size Washers and Dryers, Lounge
posting_body: Want more info on this unit?
This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 900 Sq.
Celebrate the natural beauty of the Puget Sound area when you come home to porchlight apartments in Federal Way.
This upscale property sits near Poverty Bay and close to the desirable downtown Seattle area, all while satisfying your needs for a suburban setting.
With a variety of different floor plans available for rent, you’re sure to enjoy living in one of our apartments at our Federal Way property.
Our three-bedroom apartments for rent provide space for a private balcony or patio with extra storage.
We also offer the convenience of a full-size washer/dryer in each apartment.
For more square footage, choose a two-bedroom or three-bedroom apartment with space for the entire family.
Our apartments also include open kitchens with a breakfast bar, making it easy to entertain family and friends.
Plus, you’ll find added private amenities like a wood-burning fireplace in the apartment to keep you dry during rainy WA weather.
